snippet: Kitija Laksa scored 19 points, Ariadna Pujol had 14 points and 13 rebounds, and No. 21 South Florida beat Santa Clara 63-54 on Tuesday in the Play4Kay Shootout....
lead_paragraph: Kitija Laksa scored 19 points, Ariadna Pujol had 14 points and 13 rebounds, and No. 21 South Florida beat Santa Clara 63-54 on Tuesday in the Play4Kay Shootout.

headline.main: No. 21 South Florida Women Get 1st Win in Play4Kay Shootout
